## Quality Assurance Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define quality standards for the deliverable type
- [ ] 2. Create a QA checklist tailored to the project
- [ ] 3. Conduct self-review first
- [ ] 4. Conduct peer review
- [ ] 5. Address and verify all findings
- [ ] 6. Final approval before delivery

## Key Inputs
- Deliverable: {{deliverable}}
- Quality Standards: {{quality_standards}}
- Reviewers: {{reviewers}}
- Deadline: {{deadline}}
